   313	// default zellij session rather than a bare single pane. These bars are not
   314	// implicit in zellij — a custom layout only shows them if it includes the
   315	// plugin panes explicitly, which is exactly what the built-in "default"
   316	// layout does. They render in the yyork theme colors (see internal/zellijconfig).
   317	func writeLaunchLayout(launchCmd []string, cwd string) (string, error) {
